title: Samsung Galaxy Note 5 Coming to Europe in Early 2016 If You Still Want One
text: Many of you probably know by now that Samsung has decided not to bring the Galaxy Note 5 in Europe, instead fans of the brand can only purchase the Galaxy S6 egde+ from local carriers. Obviously, there are places where you can get the Galaxy Note 5 (even the dual-SIM variant), but Samsung's hasn't officially introduced the smartphone in Europe.
